                    <span>Learning to Sail: The Annapolis Sailing School Guide for Young Sailors of All Ages by Di Goodman, et al, is a good informative reference for beginning sailors of all ages. <P>I ordered a used copy of this book through Amazon.com from ZEBOOKWORM and found its condition to be accurately described on this site. I am very satisfied with my purchase and ZEBOOKWORM's service.</span>
                  
